params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"SALES_DEPT_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"NOTE1\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"NOTE2\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"DEPO_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"TAX_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_NAME\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"TAX_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_SPEC, " +" M_CUST, " +" M_ITEM, " +" M_ORG, " +" M_TAX " +"where " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD = M_CUST.COMPANY_CD " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD = M_CUST.CUST_CD " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD = M_ORG.COMPANY_CD(+) " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.SALES_DEPT_CD = M_ORG.ORG_CD(+) " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.TAX_CD = M_TAX.TAX_CD " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_ITEM_SPEC " +"set " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUST_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"CUST_ITEM_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"SALES_DEPT_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"NOTE1\\" = ?, " +" \\"NOTE2\\" = ?, " +" \\"TAX_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"DEPO_TYP\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
" delete from " +" M_ITEM_SPEC " +"where " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" as \\"ORG_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ORG " +"where " +" M_ORG.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ORG.\\"ORG_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" a.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" a.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_ODR_CTL a, " +" T_ODR b " +"where " +" a.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and a.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" and a.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and a.odr_ctl_no = b.odr_ctl_no " +" and b.del_flg = 0"
"select " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_CUST " +"where " +" M_CUST.\\"CUST_CD\\" = ? " +" AND M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CODE\\" as \\"CODE\\", " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CODE\\" || '：' || SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CODE_NAME\\" as \\"CODE_NAME\\" " +"from " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE " +"where " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"SYS_CLASS\\" = 'SALES' " +" and SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CLASS_CODE\\" = 'PURPOSE' " +"order by " +" SYS_CLASS_CODE.\\"CODE\\""
"SELECT " +" CUST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_SALES_PLAN " +"WHERE " +" CUST_CD = ? " +" AND CUST_ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND DLT_FLG = 0"
